seo: Bifrost中间件,任意用户注册,高危漏洞
seo_en: Bifrost middleware, arbitrary user registration, high-risk vulnerability
summary: 检测Bifrost中间件是否存在任意用户注册漏洞，攻击者可通过发送特定POST请求添加管理员用户。
summary_en: Detect whether the Bifrost middleware has an arbitrary user registration vulnerability. Attackers can add administrator users by sending specific POST requests.
